      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation for the right buyer. It shows its age and would best suit someone looking for a low-cost daily driver, a backup vehicle, or a project with potential. A practical opportunity to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
