      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this car is a solid option for someone who wants affordable wheels with plenty of potential. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it has character, a comfortable cabin, and could be a great fit for a handy buyer, commuter, or anyone needing a low-cost runabout. Priced to reflect its condition and give the next owner room to make it their own.",
